OL,3,CDeath of police sergeant hit by train
OL,4,C'wholly preventable', coroner says
OL,6,FThe death of a police sergeant hit by
OL,7,Fa train while trying to help a
OL,8,Fvulnerable man was "wholly
OL,9,Fpreventable", a coroner has ruled.
OL,11,FSergeant Graham Saville, 46, who
OL,12,Fworked for Nottinghamshire Police, was
OL,13,Fon the line in Balderton, near Newark,
OL,14,FNottinghamshire, on 24 August 2023
OL,15,Fwhen he was struck by a train
OL,16,Ftravelling at up to 125mph.
