OL,3,CDeath of police sergeant hit by train
OL,4,C'wholly preventable', coroner says
OL,6,FOfficers with Sgt Saville that evening
OL,7,Frepeatedly told a police dispatcher
OL,8,Fthat the distressed man was near the
OL,9,Frailway line, Nottingham Coroner's
OL,10,FCourt heard.
OL,12,FCoroner Laurinda Bower ruled his death
OL,13,Fwas "probably more than minimally"
OL,14,Fcontributed to by a delay in the
OL,15,Fforce's control room contacting
OL,16,FNetwork Rail to tell them there were
OL,17,Fpeople on the line.
OL,19,FShe said "there were multiple missed
OL,20,Fopportunities" by his employer.
