OL,3,CDeath of police sergeant hit by train
OL,4,C'wholly preventable', coroner says
OL,6,FShe said the call came "too late for
OL,7,Fany evasive action" to be taken by
OL,8,FNetwork Rail. Had a warning been
OL,9,Fissued by the rail company to its
OL,10,Fdrivers, Sgt Saville may not have been
OL,11,Fkilled.
OL,13,FThe warning would have meant the train
OL,14,Fwould have been driven at a "crawling"
OL,15,Fspeed and would have likely been ready
OL,16,Fto stop.
OL,18,FIt would also have meant Sgt Saville
OL,19,Fwould have been more likely to see the
OL,20,Ftrain approaching.
