OL,3,CDeath of police sergeant hit by train
OL,4,C'wholly preventable', coroner says
OL,6,FShe also criticised a lack of
OL,7,F"structure" in the police force's
OL,8,Fcontrol room and training for staff,
OL,9,Fincluding when and how dispatchers
OL,10,Fshould contact Network Rail.
OL,12,FThe inquest heard that when a
OL,13,Fdispatcher finally called Network Rail
OL,14,Ffive minutes after being alerted, they
OL,15,Fdialled the public emergency helpline
OL,16,Finstead of the York Rail Operations
OL,17,FCentre and were placed on hold for
OL,18,Fminutes.
