OL,3,CDeath of police sergeant hit by train
OL,4,C'wholly preventable', coroner says
OL,6,FWhile nationally-approved railway
OL,7,Fsafety guidance was also issued to the
OL,8,Fforce and disseminated to some
OL,9,Fofficers and staff, no records were
OL,10,Fkept of who received it, who
OL,11,Fconsidered it, or whether it had been
OL,12,Funderstood.
OL,14,FMs Bower said it was "reasonably
OL,15,Fforeseeable" that officers would have
OL,16,Fto attend incidents on or near the
OL,17,Frailway line, but that risk
OL,18,Fassessments were deficient.
OL,26,@vD@VOUwD@LO]
