OL,3,CDeath of police sergeant hit by train
OL,4,C'wholly preventable', coroner says
OL,6,FThere was also no "policy or
OL,7,Fprocedure" about whether an order to
OL,8,Fstay off the tracks should be given by
OL,9,Fa senior officer in the control room.
OL,11,FThe coroner said the evidence she
OL,12,Fheard fell short of the requirements
OL,13,Fneeded for her to conclude that Sgt
OL,14,FSaville's death was unlawful, and
OL,15,Finstead made a narrative conclusion.
OL,17,FShe said there was no need for a
OL,18,Fprevention of future deaths report
OL,19,Fbecause Nottinghamshire Police had
OL,20,Fmade a raft of improvements since Sgt
OL,21,FSaville's death.
