OL,3,CDeath of police sergeant hit by train
OL,4,C'wholly preventable', coroner says
OL,6,FSgt Saville's family said the inquest
OL,7,Fprocess, which they had waited almost
OL,8,Ftwo years for, was "robust" but had
OL,9,Frevealed "shocking and disturbing
OL,10,Finformation" about Nottinghamshire
OL,11,FPolice as an organisation.
OL,13,FThey said: "Put simply, we have
OL,14,Flearned that they failed in their duty
OL,15,Fof care to protect their employees.
OL,17,F"The inquest has identified
OL,18,Fdeficiencies in so many areas, which,
OL,19,Fhad they been in place and followed,
OL,20,Fcould have prevented this tragedy
OL,21,Foccurring."
