OL,3,CDeath of police sergeant hit by train
OL,4,C'wholly preventable', coroner says
OL,6,FThey added: "What this inquest has
OL,7,Fshown us is that Graham, and his
OL,8,Fcolleagues on the ground responding to
OL,9,Fthe incident, were focused on
OL,10,Fprotecting and serving, which is what
OL,11,Fbeing a police officer is about."
OL,13,FNottinghamshire Police Federation said
OL,14,Fit was ready to work with the force to
OL,15,Fmake sure all issues raised were dealt
OL,16,Fwith.
