OL,3,CDeath of police sergeant hit by train
OL,4,C'wholly preventable', coroner says
OL,6,FFollowing Sgt Saville's death,
OL,7,Fadditional training has been provided
OL,8,Fto police officers and control room
OL,9,Fstaff about the dangers of entering
OL,10,Frailway lines, Nottinghamshire Police
OL,11,Fsaid.
OL,13,FChief Superintendent Claire Rukas,
OL,14,Fforce lead for corporate services,
OL,15,Fsaid: "We have just received the
OL,16,Fcoroner's findings and will reflect on
OL,17,Fall the points she has raised. We will
OL,18,Ftake all the necessary steps to keep
OL,19,Fthe public and our officers safe.
